0063188913", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974479_873940066522246_2661076465911733640_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=XmlFPUuR07AQ7kNvgHqV8aa&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAxtT1e1jLM-p44vMwX9fXtuXa1SkjpFVtobDOELS-Vdg&oe=66D30D1A"}, "display_name": "Playing VR with Girl Friend", "keywords": [], "long_description": "[Description]\nEnjoy the conversation with your girl friend!\nThis is a strategy game.\nPlace the units in the map using your hand.\nDestory the enemy's Base to win!\nDefeat the enemies before they destroy your Base.\n\n[How to Play]\nUse your hand or a controller to play!\nPress the button, pick up the units and release them in the map!\nThe left and right sticks allow you to move the user's position slightly.\n\n[Type of Units]\n-Base\nThis is the Base.\nBuild your Base stronger!!\n\n-Fighter\nA common flying unit.\nGround & Air Attack.\n\n-Factory\nA factory unit.\nIt generates cash.\n\n-Bomber\nA flying unit skilled for\nbombing and ground attack.\n\n-Tank\nAn anti-ground unit.\nAttacks with rapid fire.\n\n-Anti-aircraft Artillery\nA placement unit using missles.\nEffective to flying units.\n\n-Sheild\nA placement unit for defense.\nIt has high durability.\n", "short_description": "Let's play a VR video game with your girl friend!\nThis time it's a strategy game.\nPick up the units and release them in the map.\nThe units will start fighting automatically."}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "Art_1008x1440.png", "id": "4244000545622202", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974522_4244000548955535_6121386002098751284_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=AqIknaaAkwYQ7kNvgGENFcD&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBbz7d9PB4TXmXyx_r-YQnNQ9WfubR8JcyhHeeJWM0oZg&oe=66D2E285"}, {"file_name": "Art_2560x1440.png", "id": "3609745079249612", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/3897480